      "paragraphs": [
        "About The Client",
        "Our client is a leading producer of popcorn hybrids, operating at scale across global production and distribution. With deep expertise in seed development and a long-standing position in the popcorn industry, the company manages a complex operational footprint — from agronomy and production planning to inventory, sales, and global distribution. That complexity demanded a robust analytics layer capable of turning raw ERP data into actionable business intelligence. The leadership team needed a single, reliable source of truth — not another report waiting to be built."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Delayed Insights and Reactive Decision-Making"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The client's core operational data lived in Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central, but converting that data into timely, actionable insights had become a bottleneck. Reporting was heavily manual, which meant leadership was always looking at yesterday's picture of the business — never today's. The downstream effects were felt across three critical areas:"
        },
        {
          "t": "cta",
          "text": "FACING SIMILAR CHALLENGES?",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Key business areas impacted included:"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Financial performance visibility"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Sales and revenue analysis"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Inventory and operational oversight"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The cumulative effect was the same one many growing manufacturers face: decision-making that relied on delayed, fragmented, and static reports rather than real-time, insight-driven analytics."
        }
      ],
