      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Impact & Outcomes"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The implementation of Folio3's Business Central Dashboards Suite transformed the client's Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central data into a real-time, decision-enabling asset — with measurable operational and financial impact across the organization."
        },
        {
          "t": "img",
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/wph-impact-outcomes.png",
          "w": 167,
          "h": 150,
          "alt": ""
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Faster, proactive decision-making through real-time financial, sales, and inventory visibility"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Elimination of manual reporting, freeing finance and sales teams to focus on strategic analysis"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Stronger financial control with instant Budget vs. Actual tracking and expense transparency"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Improved profitability oversight via clear Gross Profit, Net Profit, and YoY performance insights"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Better inventory and cost management through aging-based inventory valuation and COGS tracking"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Aligned business execution with continuous KPI monitoring against targets and historical benchmarks"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The result: a unified, visual performance monitoring platform that improved organizational agility, strengthened financial governance, and reinforced the client's competitive position in the food manufacturing industry."
        }
      ],
